          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1660649412131-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>halved tomatoes</strong> and <strong>torn ciabatta</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>sliced shallot</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>diced chorizo</strong></p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Squeeze the <strong>halved tomatoes</strong> together with the <strong>torn ciabatta </strong>so that the juice soaks into the ciabatta – this is your <strong>marinated ciabatta</strong></p>",
