    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes have been in the oven for 15 min, remove the tray[s] from the oven and surround them with the <strong>marinated ciabatta</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a further 15 min or until the potatoes and the marinated ciabatta is golden and crispy – these are your <strong>roasted potatoes</strong> and <strong>tomato & chorizo croutons</strong></p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk so they don’t burn!</p>",
