      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong> and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>honey</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix everything together – this is your <strong>honey mustard dressing</strong></p>",
